I have been ordering choco chip temptation from Milkshake factory for the past fortnight. I enjoyed the ice cream the first two times, but today the same dessert was very disappointing. It was just a tub of vanilla with choco chips on top. There was none of the chocolate sauce and ice cream in it that we enjoyed so much.¬†
We also found pieces of plastic in our ice cream.Very disappointed in the lack of consistency.

Must try Oreo & Brownie Thick shake and Rich Brownie Temptation. My all time favourite is Oreo & Brownie thick shakes. I had ordered Nutella Brownie shake for the first time today and that was also yummy. Great Taste. Great Place.
Choco Chip Thik Milk Shake is so Tasty. Taste of choco is so chocolatey. The choco chips are crunchy. The Milk Shake is so Creamy and Delicious.

Whole searching for outlets very near to gachibowli X roads for birthday cake around 11 PM, milk shake factory came to the rescue.
Already past the closing time, We had ordered black forest birthday cake and friendly staff made the small birthday party possible at that late night hour. Cake was good enough, melted in mouth filling juices of black forest flavor all over the taste buds. We enjoyed and finished the cake within no time.
